{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778723302497,"sessionID":"ses_1dbdf3ba8ffe35GrghU06hsjLg","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"write:4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"id: hyp-20260513-002-r1s1\ntitle: Add static branch predictor (backward-taken, JAL-always-taken)\ncategory: structural\nmotivation: |\n  The current 5-stage core incurs a 1-cycle bubble on every taken branch and JAL\n  because IF always speculatively fetches PC+4. CoreMark is loop-heavy, so backward\n  branches and function calls are frequent. A static predictor that fetches the\n  target for backward branches and JAL eliminates the bubble on the common case,\n  improving IPC with negligible LUT cost (~50 LUTs) and no impact on the critical\n  path.\nhypothesis: |\n  Insert decode-and-predict logic in the IF stage. When the fetched instruction is\n  a BRANCH with a negative immediate (backward loop) or an unconditional JAL, the\n  PC is updated to the computed target instead of PC+4. A 1-bit pred_taken flag is\n  threaded through the IF/ID and ID/EX bundles. The EX stage suppresses redirect\n  when the prediction was correct; it only asserts redirect (triggering IF/ID flush)\n  on mispredict. JALR remains unpredicted. This saves one cycle per correctly\n  predicted taken branch or JAL.\nexpected_impact:\n  fitness_delta_pct: 8\n  confidence: medium\nchanges:\n  - file: rtl/core_pkg.sv\n    description: Add pred_taken bit to if_id_t and id_ex_t pipeline bundles.\n  - file: rtl/if_stage.sv\n    description: Decode BRANCH/JAL opcodes from imem_data, compute B/J immediates,\n      set predict_taken for backward branches and JAL, and select next_pc from the\n      predicted target when predict_taken is asserted.\n  - file: rtl/id_stage.sv\n    description: Thread pred_taken from the IF/ID combinational bundle into the\n      ID/EX pipeline register.\n  - file: rtl/ex_stage.sv\n    description: Replace the unconditional redirect logic with mispredict detection.\n      redirect is asserted only when a conditional branch outcome differs from\n      pred_taken, or for unpredicte JALR. Correctly predicted branches and JAL\n      no longer flush the pipeline.\n","filePath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep1/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-002-r1s1.yaml"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep1/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-002-r1s1.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-002-r1s1.yaml","time":{"start":1778723302494,"end":1778723302497}},"id":"prt_e242b7146001MZ1SPS7G3D9LEc","sessionID":"ses_1dbdf3ba8ffe35GrghU06hsjLg","messageID":"msg_e2429cbe0002Qjhi46gR2f46Wn"}}
