{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778745995064,"sessionID":"ses_1da8c0cc4ffeQEE1MMQTuelMSB","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"write:6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"id: hyp-20260514-001-r11s0\ntitle: Replace mem_stage barrel shifter with explicit byte-lane selects\ncategory: micro_opt\nmotivation: |\n  The failed MEM-to-EX load bypass hypothesis identified the variable\n  barrel shifter (dmem_rdata >> (addr*8)) as part of the critical path\n  that degraded Fmax enough to cancel IPC gains.  The current mem_stage\n  computes this 32-bit shift for every memory operation, even though\n  CoreMark is dominated by word loads (LW) which need no shifting.\n  Yosys often infers a full barrel-shifter network for the variable\n  shift pattern, adding unnecessary LUT depth on the dmem read path.\nhypothesis: |\n  Restructure mem_stage load-data extraction to eliminate the variable\n  barrel shifter.  Word loads bypass all formatting (load_data = dmem_rdata).\n  Byte loads use an explicit 4:1 byte-select mux on dmem_rdata driven by\n  addr[1:0].  Halfword loads use an explicit 2:1 halfword select.\n  Guard the shift/sign-extend logic behind in.ctrl.mem_read so it is\n  completely elided for stores.  This shortens the dmem_rdata-to-MEM/WB\n  path for the dominant LW case and reduces overall LUT depth for\n  byte/halfword accesses, improving median Fmax with zero IPC impact.\nexpected_impact:\n  fitness_delta_pct: 4\n  confidence: medium\nchanges:\n  - file: rtl/mem_stage.sv\n    description: |\n      Replace the unconditional 'shifted = dmem_rdata >> (alu_result[1:0]*8)'\n      pattern with explicit case-based byte and halfword lane extraction.\n      Word loads bypass all formatting.  Gate the load formatting logic\n      behind in.ctrl.mem_read so it is dead-code eliminated for stores.\n","filePath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep1/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-001-r11s0.yaml"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep1/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-001-r11s0.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-001-r11s0.yaml","time":{"start":1778745995050,"end":1778745995063}},"id":"prt_e2585cbba001HVR4iuMasWBiaP","sessionID":"ses_1da8c0cc4ffeQEE1MMQTuelMSB","messageID":"msg_e258575050018M39rUO6WtBQv9"}}
