ns, a minimal 32-entry 2-bit BHT (64 flops) still recovers +7.3% fitness by predicting forward conditional branches; forward-branch direction is the largest remaining dynamic bubble source in CoreMark.\"}\n","exit":0,"description":"Find current best hypothesis details","truncated":false},"title":"Find current best hypothesis details","time":{"start":1778753490514,"end":1778753490516}},"id":"prt_e25f84af5001uzu6Yz5GWZxW3B","sessionID":"ses_1da08a9b3ffeiE0K02BupWfSfi","messageID":"msg_e25f83723001nqGx1v643D6fA8"}}
