{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778747957820,"sessionID":"ses_1da61a41affeTX9L0P7xbsplOu","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"id: hyp-20260514-003-r12s2\ntitle: \"Add 4-entry return-address stack for JALR prediction\"\ncategory: predictor\nmotivation: |\n  The current predictor correctly handles conditional branches (32-entry BHT)\n  and JAL (always-taken), but JALR is never predicted. Every function return\n  causes a 2-cycle redirect bubble in EX. CoreMark contains many small function\n  calls; a return-address stack predicts return targets with near-perfect\n  accuracy for a tiny area cost (~130 flops), improving IPC without degrading\n  Fmax.\nhypothesis: |\n  Add a 4-entry return-address stack (RAS) to the IF stage. Push PC+4 on\n  any JAL or JALR call (rd = x1/x5). Pop the RAS and predict taken on any\n  JALR return (rd = x0, rs1 = x1/x5). Thread the predicted target through a\n  new `pred_target` field in the IF/ID and ID/EX bundles. In EX stage,\n  compare the actual JALR target with `pred_target`; only redirect on\n  mispredict or when JALR was not predicted. This eliminates the redirect\n  bubble on correct function returns.\nexpected_impact:\n  fitness_delta_pct: 4\n  confidence: medium\nchanges:\n  - file: rtl/core_pkg.sv\n    description: \"Add `pred_target` field to `if_id_t` and `id_ex_t` structs.\"\n  - file: rtl/if_stage.sv\n    description: \"Add 4-entry RAS with push/pop control; use RAS top as predicted target for JALR returns; drive `out.pred_target`.\"\n  - file: rtl/id_stage.sv\n    description: \"Thread `in.pred_target` into the ID/EX register.\"\n  - file: rtl/ex_stage.sv\n    description: \"Replace unconditional JALR redirect with mispredict detection using `in.pred_target`; only redirect when JALR was not predicted or target mismatches.\"\n","filePath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep1/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-003-r12s2.yaml"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep1/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-003-r12s2.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-003-r12s2.yaml","time":{"start":1778747957804,"end":1778747957818}},"id":"prt_e25a38b02001tNSVq1eEitghkZ","sessionID":"ses_1da61a41affeTX9L0P7xbsplOu","messageID":"msg_e259e5c1f001SXEfunjrQcVQjX"}}
