ts not-taken on\\\\nthe last iteration, removing the only remaining systematic direction\\\\nmispredictions with only ~100 flops and no wider BHT mux.\\\\n\\\",\\n  \\\"hypothesis\\\": \\\"Add an 8-entry direct-mapped loop predictor table to the IF stage.\\\\nEach entry stores a tag, a trained iteration length, a speculative\\\\ndown-counter, and a 1-bit confidence flag.\\\\nWhen a backward branch is fetched, if the entry is valid, tag matches,\\\\nand confidence is high, the predictor overrides the BHT:\\\\n  - down-counter > 0  \\\\u2192 predict taken and decrement the counter.\\\\n  - down-counter == 0 \\\\u2192 predict not-taken.\\\\nIn EX, resolved backward branches update the table:\\\\n  - During training (confidence low) the table counts taken outcomes;\\\\n    the first not-taken exit stores the count as the trained length\\\\n    and sets confidence high.\\\\n  - On a correct exit (predicted not-taken) the counter ... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n57: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1778745629207,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1da8c0d24ffeyR5lnSLdShWPv7\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e25805a160011SRzb7swUMDrXf\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"6ef4ad46810c40172e11a19e9d966c945fe33d2d\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e25801f22001MKrALnCg1JJ6yr\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1da8c0d24ffeyR5lnSLdShWPv7\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":94903,\"input\":1240,\"output\":79,\"reasoning\":144,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":93440}},\"cost\":0.0170204}}\n58: {\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1778745635737,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1da8c0d24ffeyR5lnSLdShWPv7\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e25807396001bpVQhz7PqwhsnI\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e25805a38001fXHB8y10Avutr5\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1da8c0d24ffeyR5lnSLdShWPv7\",\"snapshot\":\"6ef4ad46810c40172e11a19e9d966c945fe33d2d\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n59: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1778745640225,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1da8c0d24ffeyR5lnSLdShWPv7\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e25807690001szfOY87xlCDl1f\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e25805a38001fXHB8y10Avutr5\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1da8c0d24ffeyR5lnSLdShWPv7\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Hypothesis written to:\\n\\n`cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-003-r11s2.yaml`\\n\\n**Summary:** Add an 8-entry loop predictor to the IF stage that learns the iteration count of backward branches and predicts not-taken on the final loop exit. This targets the last systematic direction misprediction source that the existing 32-entry BHT cannot fix (loop exits), with minimal area (~100 flops) and no widening of the BHT read mux.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1778745636496,\"end\":1778745640222}}}\n60: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1778745640298,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1da8c0d24ffeyR5lnSLdShWPv7\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e2580856900110HcbgMjjXUZF2\",\"reason\":\"stop\",\"snapshot\":\"6ef4ad46810c40172e11a19e9d966c945fe33d2d\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e25805a38001fXHB8y10Avutr5\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1da8c0d24ffeyR5lnSLdShWPv7\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":95685,\"input\":1093,\"output\":105,\"reasoning\":23,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":94464}},\"cost\":0.01666459}}\n\n(End of file - total 60 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1778744824258,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1da8c0d24ffeyR5lnSLdShWPv7\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e257411bf001GSCm9nJYwA0TL8\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e2573f313001bNRPmxRGqKVY1i\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1da8c0d24ffeyR5lnSLdShWPv7\",\"snapshot\":\"6ef4ad46810c40172e11a19e9d966c945fe33d2d\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1778744836736,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1da8c0d24ffeyR5lnSLdShWPv7\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"grep\",\"callID\":\"grep:0\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"RAS|return address|jalr\",\"path\":\"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep1/cores/bench/experiments/log.jsonl\"},\"output\":\"Found 3 matches\\n/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep1/cores/bench/experiments/log.jsonl:\\n  Line 7: {\\\"id\\\": \\\"hyp-20260513-003-r2s2\\\", \\\"title\\\": \\\"Add 4-entry Return Address Stack for JALR return prediction\\\", \\\"category\\\": \\\"predictor\\\", \\\"motivation\\\": \\\"The existing static predictor eliminates bubbles for backward branches and\\\\nunconditional JAL, but every JALR (function return) still incurs a 1-cycle\\\\nflush because the target is unknown until EX. CoreMark contains frequent\\\\nnested function calls, so returns are a noticeable fraction of the dynamic\\\\ninstruction stream. A tiny Return Address Stack (RAS) pushes the link\\\\naddress on JAL-to-x1/x5 and pops it on JALR-from-x1/x5, predicting the\\\\nreturn target in IF with high accuracy at negligible area cost.\\\\n\\\", \\\"hypothesis\\\": {\\\"motivation\\\": \\\"The existing static predictor eliminates bubbles for backward branches and\\\\nunconditional JAL, but every JALR (function return) still incurs a 1-cycle\\\\nflush because the target is unknown until EX. CoreMark contains frequent\\\\nnested function calls, so returns are a noticeable fraction of the dynamic\\\\ninstruction stream. A tiny Return Address Stack (RAS) pushes the link\\\\naddress on JAL-to-x1/x5 and pops it on JALR-from-x1/x5, predicting the\\\\nreturn target in IF with high accuracy at negligible area cost.\\\\n\\\", \\\"hypothesis\\\": \\\"Extend the IF-stage predictor with a 4-entry RAS. When the fetched\\\\ninstruction is a JAL with rd=x1 or x5, push PC+4 onto the stack. When the\\\\nfetched instruction is a JALR with rs1=x1 or x5 and the stack is non-empty,\\\\npop the top entry and treat it ... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1778744840518,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1da8c0d24ffeyR5lnSLdShWPv7\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e257451440014OmZdH9lQsusLv\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"6ef4ad46810c40172e11a19e9d966c945fe33d2d\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e2573f313001bNRPmxRGqKVY1i\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1da8c0d24ffeyR5lnSL