{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778749860981,"sessionID":"ses_1da496ea7ffezAxTBNo3MtwKnx","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"id: hyp-20260514-003-r13s2\ntitle: Hash-mix higher PC bits into 32-entry BHT index to reduce aliasing\ncategory: predictor\nmotivation: |\n  The 32-entry 2-bit saturating-counter BHT is the proven sweet spot for\n  this core, delivering a +7.3% fitness gain. A follow-up attempt to grow\n  the table to 128 entries regressed -3% because the wider read mux hurt\n  Fmax, while gshare global-history variants regressed due to history\n  staleness. The remaining occasional forward-branch mispredictions may\n  stem from destructive aliasing among branches that share the low five\n  PC bits. A zero-cost hash that XORs higher PC bits into the index\n  scatters colliding branches without enlarging the array or adding any\n  new state.\nhypothesis: |\n  Keep the proven 32-entry 2-bit saturating-counter table unchanged, but\n  change both the read index and the write-back index from pc[6:2] to\n  pc[6:2] ^ pc[11:7]. In the IF stage this mixes bits 7-11 of the PC\n  into the existing 5-bit index, reducing the chance that two branches\n  whose lower five bits collide map to the same counter. In the EX stage\n  the update index uses in.pc[6:2] ^ in.pc[11:7] so the counter write\n  hits exactly the entry that was read during fetch. The combinational\n  cost is a single 5-bit XOR, which Yosys will absorb into the existing\n  LUT fabric with negligible Fmax impact. No new flops, pipeline bundles,\n  or control signals are introduced.\nexpected_impact:\n  fitness_delta_pct: 2\n  confidence: medium\nchanges:\n  - file: rtl/if_stage.sv\n    description: Change BHT read index from pc[6:2] to pc[6:2] ^ pc[11:7].\n  - file: rtl/ex_stage.sv\n    description: Change BHT update index from in.pc[6:2] to in.pc[6:2] ^ in.pc[11:7].\n","filePath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep1/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-003-r13s2.yaml"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep1/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-003-r13s2.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-003-r13s2.yaml","time":{"start":1778749860975,"end":1778749860981}},"id":"prt_e25c0c5cf001kA8E1xqd5yL6nZ","sessionID":"ses_1da496ea7ffezAxTBNo3MtwKnx","messageID":"msg_e25be147f001QwUB6vN8Zf28Oq"}}
