ount, conf), combinational read/decrement, and integrate with predict_taken so a matching confident entry overrides the BHT for backward branches.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/ex_stage.sv\", \"description\": \"Add loop-predictor update logic: on resolved backward branches allocate/train entries, reload counters on correct exits, and clear confidence on mispredicts. Drive update signals back to IF.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/core_pkg.sv\", \"description\": \"Add loop_predictor_entry_t struct and confidence constants to the package.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/core.sv\", \"description\": \"Wire the new loop-predictor update signals between ex_stage and if_stage.\"}]}, \"expected_impact\": {\"fitness_delta_pct\": 3, \"confidence\": \"medium\"}, \"changes\": [{\"file\": \"rtl/if_stage.sv\", \"description\": \"Add 8-entry loop-predictor array (tag, length, count, conf), combinational read/decrement, and integrate with predict_taken so a matching confident entry overrides the BHT for backward branches.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/ex_stage.sv\", \"description\": \"Add loop-predictor update logic: on resolved backward branches allocate/train entries, reload counters on correct exits, and clear confidence on mispredicts. Drive update signals back to IF.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/core_pkg.sv\", \"description\": \"Add loop_predictor_entry_t struct and confidence constants to the package.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/core.sv\", \"description\": \"Wire the new loop-predictor update signals between ex_stage and if_stage.\"}], \"outcome\": \"regression\", \"fitness\": 302.03, \"delta_pct\": -13.15, \"vs_baseline\": 6.79, \"fmax_mhz\": 126.68, \"ipc_coremark\": 2e-06, \"cycles\": 4194286, \"iterations\": 10, \"lut4\": 10454, \"ff\": 1951, \"seeds\": [114.19, 126.68, 139.82], \"formal_passed\": true, \"cosim_passed\": true, \"error\": null, \"implementation_notes\": \"\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-14T08:24:35.661190Z\", \"slot\": 2, \"round_id\": 11, \"scribe_skipped\": \"PermissionError: scribe rewrote /Users/bonetto/bonet