r-perfect\\naccuracy for a tiny area cost (~130 flops), improving IPC without degrading\\nFmax.\\n\", \"hypothesis\": \"Add a 4-entry return-address stack (RAS) to the IF stage. Push PC+4 on\\nany JAL or JALR call (rd = x1/x5). Pop the RAS and predict taken on any\\nJALR return (rd = x0, rs1 = x1/x5). Thread the predicted target through a\\nnew `pred_target` field in the IF/ID and ID/EX bundles. In EX stage,\\ncompare the actual JALR target with `pred_target`; only redirect on\\nmispredict or when JALR was not predicted. This eliminates the redirect\\nbubble on correct function returns.\\n\", \"expected_impact\": {\"fitness_delta_pct\": 4, \"confidence\": \"medium\"}, \"changes\": [{\"file\": \"rtl/core_pkg.sv\", \"description\": \"Add `pred_target` field to `if_id_t` and `id_ex_t` structs.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/if_stage.sv\", \"description\": \"Add 4-entry RAS with push/pop control; use RAS top as predicted target for JALR returns; drive `out.pred_target`.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/id_stage.sv\", \"description\": \"Thread `in.pred_target` into the ID/EX register.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/ex_stage.sv\", \"description\": \"Replace unconditional JALR redirect with mispredict detection using `in.pred_target`; only redirect when JALR was not predicted or target mismatches.\"}]}, \"expected_impact\": {\"fitness_delta_pct\": 4, \"confidence\": \"medium\"}, \"changes\": [{\"file\": \"rtl/core_pkg.sv\", \"description\": \"Add `pred_target` field to `if_id_t` and `id_ex_t` structs.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/if_stage.sv\", \"description\": \"Add 4-entry RAS with push/pop control; use RAS top as predicted target for JALR returns; drive `out.pred_target`.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/id_stage.sv\", \"description\": \"Thread `in.pred_target` into the ID/EX register.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/ex_stage.sv\", \"description\": \"Replace unconditional JALR redirect with mispredict detection using `in.pred_target`; only redirect when JALR was not predicted or target mismatches.\"}], \"outcome\": \"regression\", 