{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778731854099,"sessionID":"ses_1db556982ffeOpDgGDUzASRGrB","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"write:5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"id: hyp-20260514-003-r5s2\ntitle: Expand BHT to 128 entries to reduce aliasing among forward branches\ncategory: predictor\nmotivation: |\n  The existing 32-entry 2-bit BHT recovered +7.3% fitness by learning forward\n  branch directions, but with only 32 entries branches whose lower PC bits\n  collide alias destructively. In the 6 KB CoreMark working set this is not\n  uncommon, leaving a noticeable fraction of forward-branch bubbles unresolved.\n  Expanding the table to 128 entries (index PC[8:2]) keeps the proven\n  saturating-counter structure intact while cutting aliasing, at a cost of\n  only 192 additional flops and minimal LUT overhead.\nhypothesis: |\n  Replace the 32-entry BHT in if_stage with a 128-entry direct-mapped BHT.\n  Change the index from pc[6:2] to pc[8:2] (7 bits) and widen the\n  bht_update_idx port from 5 to 7 bits so EX can write back using in.pc[8:2].\n  The counter update rule, strong-taken initialization, and interaction with\n  the static backward-taken / JAL predictor remain exactly the same. No new\n  pipeline bundles or control signals are introduced, making this a very low-\n  risk resize of a component that is already known to work.\nexpected_impact:\n  fitness_delta_pct: 3\n  confidence: high\nchanges:\n  - file: rtl/core.sv\n    description: Widen bht_update_idx from 5 to 7 bits to match the 128-entry table index.\n  - file: rtl/if_stage.sv\n    description: >\n      Enlarge the bht array to [0:127], update the init loop bound to 128,\n      and change the read index from pc[6:2] to pc[8:2].\n  - file: rtl/ex_stage.sv\n    description: >\n      Change bht_update_idx from in.pc[6:2] to in.pc[8:2] so resolved\n      branches write back to the correct 128-entry slot.\n","filePath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep1/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-003-r5s2.yaml"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep1/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-003-r5s2.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-003-r5s2.yaml","time":{"start":1778731854090,"end":1778731854098}},"id":"prt_e24ae0a810010S7OdtITNFLSNI","sessionID":"ses_1db556982ffeOpDgGDUzASRGrB","messageID":"msg_e24ad1f67002zaqRj2LkYxn0hG"}}
